---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Aadit Agrawal | Codex Consultant, Student, Infra, Dev, AI Stuff">
    <section id="about" class="section intro-section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2 class="label-text">About</h2>
            <div class="line"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="intro-copy">
            <h2>I like figuring out tech by making things with it.</h2>
            <p>
                I'm a CS student at MIT Manipal and a Codex consultant at
                OpenAI India. Mostly I'm a generalist (infra, AI, developer
                tools, the occasional research prototype), but the part I
                actually love is making things people end up using: campus
                tools half the college quietly relies on, small scripts, and
                services I host myself and tend to like a garden.
            </p>
            <p>
                These days that means consulting on Codex and agentic
                developer workflows, leading a student research lab at MAHE
                (<a href="https://ecitis.org">CASIR</a>), and keeping an
                on-prem inference stack alive across Apple Silicon, Blackwell,
                and CUDA. When I step away from that I'm usually self-hosting
                something new, writing on
                <a href="https://blog.ecitis.org">blog.ecitis.org</a>, or
                building with friends.
            </p>
            <p class="intro-close">
                I grew up on science fiction. Asimov, Sagan, Andy Weir. I think
                that's where the building comes from: a quiet conviction that
                careful engineering is a kind of optimism.
            </p>
        </div>

        <p class="next-step">
            There's a longer story in <a href="/projects/">/projects</a> and
            <a href="/experience/">/experience</a>. Or just say hi.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="section contact-section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2 class="label-text">Contact</h2>
            <div class="line"></div>
        </div>

        <p class="contact-lead">
            The fastest way to reach me is email. I read everything, and I
            answer the thoughtful ones.
        </p>

        <div class="contact-actions font-mono">
            <a href="mailto:mail@aaditagrawal.com">mail@aaditagrawal.com</a>
            <a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-resume" data-resume-open>resume.pdf</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/aaditagrawal">github</a>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/aadit-agrawal">linkedin</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    .intro-section {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .intro-copy {
        max-width: 60ch;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--space-md);
    }

    .intro-copy h2 {
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 2.6vw, 2.4rem);
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 1.12;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        max-width: 18ch;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
        color: var(--text-display);
    }

    .intro-copy p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        font-size: 1.0625rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .intro-close {
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-size: 1.25rem !important;
        line-height: 1.5 !important;
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--text-secondary) !important;
        padding-top: var(--space-sm);
    }

    .next-step {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-size: 1.0625rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        max-width: 60ch;
    }

    .next-step a {
        color: var(--text-primary);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-visible);
        transition: color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease), border-color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease);
    }

    .next-step a:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
        border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
    }

    .contact-lead {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-size: 1.0625rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        max-width: 52ch;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .contact-actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: var(--space-sm) var(--space-xl);
        font-size: 0.9375rem;
    }

    .contact-actions a {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        transition: color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease);
    }

    .contact-actions a:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
    }
</style>
